'''Nihilism''' is the [[Some argue|purported]] [[Philosophy|ideology]] of [[Anonymous]] and the backbone of [[Encyclopedia Dramatica]]. When applied in [[England|practise]], nihilism becomes the sweet philosophical nectar from which all [[win]] flows forth. Wielding this black person weapon of thought against one's [[retard|enemy]] will bring much [[lulz|joy]] and will harden the hearts of any [[troll|man]]. It is well known that [[women]] can't be [[men|nihilist]] because they are [[emo]]tional, get easily [[butthurt|saddened]], and are thus made of disgusting [[fail]]. This is why they belong [[in the kitchen|where they are most comfortable]]. It is fact that only virgins think this way.
==Argument for Nihilism==
Nihilism is the demiurge of all philosophy, and is the engine that moves [[13 year old boys|men]] to do [[troll|great deeds]]. There hasn't been a [[raid]] around that didn't harness this concept to fight the scourge of [[unwarranted self-importance]] on the [[internets]]. It asserts that [[noone]] and [[nothing]] is important, and thus subject to intense [[pwn|ridicule]] whenever [[you|they]] get too [[Unwarrented self-importance|big for their britches]]. So [[lulz|laugh]] at that [[feminazi]], mock the [[Fred Phelps|bigots]], and spit in the face of [[Scientology|religion]]. You are [[Doing it wrong|doing the right thing]], [[sick fuck|buddy]].

==Argument against Nihilism==
Although the [[Win|positive factors]] that can be derived from nihilism are great and vast, the practice of nihilism ultimately leads to a [[Time paradox|paradox]]: Acknowledging [[You|one's self]] that nothing at all has any value whatsoever, yet continuing to live life. As a result of such [[Shit bricks|mindfuckery]], a [[13-year old boy|nihilist]] will be [[Goatse|completely open]] to becoming [[an hero]], [[Drug|OD'ing on drugs]], being butt pirates & giving each other reach arounds or any other form of unwillingness to care for oneself.

==Offending Nihilists==
Even though, it is physically impossible to offend a nihilist, it's very easy to offend a nihilist mentally since they're just narrow-minded fucktards who want the world to go their way. Much [[lulz]] can be generated this way, and it can prove an especially effective [[tool]] for starting a [[flame war]] deep within the [[anus|bowels]] of the [[LGBT]] community.

